*(Screenshots will be added in `/screenshots` folder)*

## 🧠 Key Concepts Demonstrated
- VPN tunneling and encryption
- Certificate-based authentication
- Firewall rule logic and NAT
- Packet inspection for security validation

## 🧪 Challenges & Solutions
| Issue | Resolution |
|------|------------|
| Tunnel failed to establish | Corrected firewall rule to allow UDP 1194 |
| DNS leaks detected | Enabled DNS override in OpenVPN settings |
| Certificate mismatch | Regenerated client cert with correct CN |

## 📁 Files Included
- `server.conf`: OpenVPN server config
- `client.ovpn`: Client profile
- `firewall-rules.txt`: pfSense rule export
- `wireshark-capture.pcap`: Sample packet capture

